# Entra Connect Troubleshooting Module

**Author:** Adrian Johnson (adrian207@gmail.com)  
**Version:** 1.0.0  
**Date:** December 2024

This module provides diagnostics, automated repair, and troubleshooting capabilities for Entra Connect.

## Functions

### Test-EntraConnectConnectivity
Tests connectivity to Azure services.

### Diagnose-EntraConnectSyncIssues
Diagnoses synchronization problems.

### Repair-EntraConnectConfiguration
Automatically repairs common configuration issues.

### Test-EntraConnectAuthentication
Tests authentication methods.

### Diagnose-EntraConnectPerformance
Identifies performance bottlenecks.

### Repair-EntraConnectSyncErrors
Automatically fixes sync errors.

### Test-EntraConnectSecurity
Validates security configurations.

### Diagnose-EntraConnectConnectivity
Diagnoses network connectivity issues.

### Repair-EntraConnectPermissions
Fixes permission-related issues.

### Test-EntraConnectHealth
Comprehensive health check.
